trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of connections for a control in a Web Parts zone.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling med tilkoblingene for en kontroll i en webdeler sone.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: A control in a Web Parts zone can act as a consumer of data from another control or as a provider of data to other controls.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll i en webdeler sone kan fungere som forbruker av data fra en annen kontroll eller som en leverandør av data til andre kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class represents a collection of those connections.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen representerer en samling med tilkoblingene.

trans-unit.source: Typically, an instance of this class is returned from a property such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Connections%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis er en forekomst av denne klassen returnert fra en egenskap for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Connections%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Connections%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can iterate through the collection in the same way you would any collection, and you can search for a particular connection using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.ID%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan gå gjennom samlingen i på samme måte som du vil en samling, og du kan søke etter en bestemt tilkobling ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.ID%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adds a member to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til et medlem i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to add a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å legge til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objekt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>

trans-unit.source: The object is added to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som legges til slutten av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: To add an object at a specific location in the collection, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection.Insert%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til et objekt på et spesifikt sted i samlingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection.Insert%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> to be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> som skal legges til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer indicating the index where the connection will be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir indeksen der tilkoblingen blir lagt til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> object is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objektet er i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to determine whether a particular connection is contained in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å fastslå om en bestemt tilkobling ligger i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection>

trans-unit.source: This method is commonly used to test for the existence of a connection before performing a task, such as adding a connection to or removing one from a collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes vanligvis til å teste for forekomsten av en tilkobling før du utfører en oppgave, for eksempel legge til en tilkobling til eller fjerne et fra en samling.

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection"></xref> collection to an array, starting at a particular array index.

trans-unit.source: The specified array must be of a compatible type.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte matrisen må være kompatibelt.

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Elementene kopieres til den <xref:System.Array>i samme rekkefølge som enumeratoren går gjennom den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionCollection> </xref:System.Array>
